00:17:11.540 --> 00:17:12.540
[Guest]: Probably they're on the way.

00:17:12.540 --> 00:17:17.900
[Guest]: You know, I mean, there are talks of a dengue vaccine among some researchers.

00:17:17.900 --> 00:17:23.980
[Guest]: Many of these things float around as ideas for about 10-20 years, lots of research happens,

00:17:23.980 --> 00:17:26.180
[Guest]: eventually something hits the market.

00:17:26.180 --> 00:17:31.420
[Guest]: So I think the time is right for a few drugs to, few medicines to start coming out of India

00:17:31.420 --> 00:17:33.220
[Guest]: for India.

00:17:33.220 --> 00:17:39.740
[Guest]: And I think once we see a few of them successful, you know, I think the constituency for more

00:17:39.740 --> 00:17:42.660
[Guest]: reward policymaking on this will only grow.

